1777:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Helper macro to calculate the temperature (unit: degree Celsius)
1778:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         from ADC conversion data of internal temperature sensor.
1779:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Computation is using temperature sensor calibration values
1780:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         stored in system memory for each device during production.
1781:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Calculation formula:
ARM GAS  /tmp/ccikHvDC.s 			page 290


1782:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           Temperature = ((TS_ADC_DATA - TS_CAL1)
1783:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                           * (TS_CAL2_TEMP - TS_CAL1_TEMP))
1784:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                         / (TS_CAL2 - TS_CAL1) + TS_CAL1_TEMP
1785:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           with TS_ADC_DATA = temperature sensor raw data measured by ADC
1786:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                Avg_Slope = (TS_CAL2 - TS_CAL1)
1787:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                            / (TS_CAL2_TEMP - TS_CAL1_TEMP)
1788:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                TS_CAL1   = equivalent TS_ADC_DATA at temperature
1789:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                            TEMP_DEGC_CAL1 (calibrated in factory)
1790:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                TS_CAL2   = equivalent TS_ADC_DATA at temperature
1791:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                            TEMP_DEGC_CAL2 (calibrated in factory)
1792:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Caution: Calculation relevancy under reserve that calibration
1793:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                  parameters are correct (address and data).
1794:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                  To calculate temperature using temperature sensor
1795:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                  datasheet typical values (generic values less, therefore
1796:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                  less accurate than calibrated values),
