1802:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         and ADC helper macro @ref __LL_ADC_CALC_VREFANALOG_VOLTAGE().
1803:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, calibration data of temperature sensor
1804:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         corresponds to a resolution of 12 bits,
1805:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         this is the recommended ADC resolution to convert voltage of
