3224:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         "fully configurable" or "not fully configurable"
3225:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         are available, they can be chosen using
3226:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         function @ref LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerConfigurable().
3227:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         This function can be used with setting "not fully configurable".
3228:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Refer to description of functions @ref LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerConfigurable()
