3307:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Add channel to ADC group regular sequence: channel on rank corresponding to
3308:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         channel number.
3309:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   This function performs:
3310:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - Channels ordering into each rank of scan sequence:
3311:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           rank of each channel is fixed by channel HW number
3312:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           (channel 0 fixed on rank 0, channel 1 fixed on rank1, ...).
3313:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - Set channels selected by adding them to the current sequencer
3314:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           configuration.
3315:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, ADC group regular sequencer both modes
3316:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         "fully configurable" or "not fully configurable"
3317:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         are available, they can be chosen using
3318:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         function @ref LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerConfigurable().
3319:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         This function can be used with setting "not fully configurable".
3320:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Refer to description of functions @ref LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerConfigurable()
3321:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         and @ref LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerLength().
3322:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, after modifying sequencer (functions
3323:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @ref LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerLength()
3324:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @ref LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerRanks(), ...)
3325:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         it is mandatory to wait for the assertion of CCRDY flag
3326:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         using @ref LL_ADC_IsActiveFlag_CCRDY().
3327:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Otherwise, some actions may be ignored.
3328:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Refer to description of @ref LL_ADC_IsActiveFlag_CCRDY
3329:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         for more details.
3330:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Depending on devices and packages, some channels may not be available.
3331:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Refer to device datasheet for channels availability.
3332:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, to measure internal channels (VrefInt,
3333:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         TempSensor, ...), measurement paths to internal channels must be
3334:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         enabled separately.
3335:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         This can be done using function @ref LL_ADC_SetCommonPathInternalCh().
3336:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, setting of this feature is conditioned to
3337:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC state:
3338:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC must be disabled or enabled without conversion on going
3339:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         on group regular.
3340:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   One or several values can be selected.
3341:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Example: (LL_ADC_CHANNEL_4 | LL_ADC_CHANNEL_12 | ...)
