4225:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h **** /**
4226:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set ADC analog watchdog threshold value of threshold
4227:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         high or low.
4228:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   If values of both thresholds high or low must be set,
4229:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         use function @ref LL_ADC_ConfigAnalogWDThresholds().
4230:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   In case of ADC resolution different of 12 bits,
4231:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         analog watchdog thresholds data require a specific shift.
4232:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Use helper macro @ref __LL_ADC_ANALOGWD_SET_THRESHOLD_RESOLUTION().
4233:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, there are 2 kinds of analog watchdog
4234:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         instance:
4235:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - AWD standard (instance AWD1):
4236:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - channels monitored: can monitor 1 channel or all channels.
4237:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - groups monitored: ADC group regular.
4238:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - resolution: resolution is not limited (corresponds to
4239:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             ADC resolution configured).
4240:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - AWD flexible (instances AWD2, AWD3):
4241:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - channels monitored: flexible on channels monitored, selection is
4242:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             channel wise, from from 1 to all channels.
4243:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             Specificity of this analog watchdog: Multiple channels can
4244:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             be selected. For example:
